        <item>
          <title>Blue Jays put 3-time Cy Young Award winner Max Scherzer on IL because of right thumb inflammation</title>
          <description><![CDATA[TORONTO (AP) — The Toronto Blue Jays put right-hander Max Scherzer on the 15-day injured list Sunday because of inflammation in his right thumb. The move comes one day after the three-time Cy Young Award winner left his debut start with Toronto after three innings because of right lat soreness.]]></description>
